1. Execute command after navigating to the following directory
        cd src/Scripts

2. python SampleSpec.py > ./../../reports.html

Different ways of executing the files under package
------------------------------------------------------
1. C:\Bhadri\Automation_Projects\Python_Automation_Project\src\Scripts> pytest --driver=Firefox --html=report.html --self-contained-html
Executes all scripts available under Scripts directory.

2.	C:\Bhadri\Automation_Projects\Python_Automation_Project\src\Scripts>pytest -k "test" --driver=Firefox --html=report.html --self-contained-html
Executes all scripts with name “test” under Scripts directory.

3.	C:\Bhadri\Automation_Projects\Python_Automation_Project>pytest src\Scripts\test_faceBook_login.py --driver=Firefox
Executes only specified script.
